=====
sites
=====

Yet another attempt to get my various sites under control.

Layout
======

To keep things sane, all the sites go in `sites/<hostname>`.

I intend on using mkdocs_ for most things, if possible. I recommend installing
it with the pipsi_ wrapper around pip_.

.. _mkdocs: http://www.mkdocs.org/
.. _pipsi: https://github.com/mitsuhiko/pipsi
.. _pip: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip

.. vim:set ft=rst:
